<p>Others liked his take on the word, with one saying: 'I like the way Osher says covid. So fancy' while another echoed:  'Osher, but why do you say “Co-Vid” like “covid” it makes sound so fancy.'  </p>

<p>Meanwhile, Wednesday's episode saw Locky send home Izzy Sharman-Firth and intruder Bec Cvilikas at the rose ceremony. </p>

